WEBVTT

01:31.380 --> 01:34.900
=Generation to Generation=

01:35.020 --> 01:37.900
=Episode 24=

01:54.130 --> 01:55.820
Zigui is finally free.

01:56.740 --> 01:57.620
All these years,

01:58.770 --> 02:00.100
he was plagued by injuries,

02:01.570 --> 02:02.690
homeless,

02:03.540 --> 02:04.900
and hunted by his own sect.

02:06.930 --> 02:09.060
He suffered too much.

02:09.500 --> 02:11.850
It was no easy feat
for Uncle Guo to survive.

02:14.130 --> 02:16.540
Why did Yin Dai insist on killing him?

02:17.500 --> 02:18.610
Yin Dai claimed

02:20.340 --> 02:22.220
Zigui signed a surrender letter

02:23.170 --> 02:24.410
and disgraced the sect.

02:25.730 --> 02:26.570
If you ask me,

02:27.260 --> 02:29.060
he just didn't want Zigui to return.

02:29.720 --> 02:30.570
Otherwise,

02:30.570 --> 02:31.690
how could the Guos' estate

02:31.690 --> 02:33.980
so rightfully fall
into Qingque Sect's hands?

02:35.570 --> 02:36.730
The Yins' grand residence

02:37.380 --> 02:38.690
and the Double Lotus Palace

02:39.290 --> 02:40.890
were both built after that.

03:22.980 --> 03:24.820
Yin Dai was after the Ziwei Method.

03:25.690 --> 03:28.016
Using Nie Hengcheng's slaughter
of innocents as an excuse,

03:28.290 --> 03:29.410
he incited the Six Sects

03:30.010 --> 03:30.980
to attack Li Sect.

03:31.220 --> 03:32.220
His true purpose

03:32.690 --> 03:33.690
was to find out

03:33.690 --> 03:35.850
why Nie Hengcheng's power
had grown so greatly.

03:38.380 --> 03:39.780
He even sacrificed his disciples

03:40.170 --> 03:41.380
to capture Elder Kaiyang,

03:41.810 --> 03:42.660
and as he wished,

03:42.660 --> 03:44.290
obtained the Ziwei Method.

03:44.850 --> 03:45.690
From then on,

03:46.220 --> 03:47.753
new and old grudges between both sides

03:47.940 --> 03:48.890
ran deep,

03:49.610 --> 03:50.780
like fire and water.

03:52.610 --> 03:54.570
And he could begin his next move.

03:56.610 --> 03:57.570
Stop.

04:01.060 --> 04:01.900
Zhao,

04:03.380 --> 04:05.130
do you know why your aunt

04:05.540 --> 04:06.980
went alone to kill Nie Hengcheng?

04:07.500 --> 04:08.940
Yin Dai knew his scheme

04:09.820 --> 04:11.730
would one day be exposed by your aunt,

04:12.820 --> 04:14.326
but he calculated one thing precisely,

04:14.730 --> 04:16.170
and that was her character.

04:16.980 --> 04:18.540
She could never stand by while Jianghu

04:18.540 --> 04:20.410
was full of blood and corpses.

04:21.900 --> 04:22.810
So, Yin Dai tricked her

04:22.810 --> 04:24.340
into cultivating the Disintegration.

04:25.129 --> 04:27.125
That way, he could kill
two birds with one stone.

04:27.170 --> 04:28.850
- Shut up.
- He got rid

04:28.850 --> 04:31.140
of Nie Hengcheng and your aunt.

04:35.900 --> 04:36.740
That is the truth.

04:37.020 --> 04:37.860
You can't hide

04:38.410 --> 04:39.250
or escape it.

04:44.120 --> 04:45.433
Blades are to be welded steadily,

04:45.780 --> 04:46.873
but your heart is in chaos.

04:47.540 --> 04:48.520
How can you wield it now?

04:49.610 --> 04:51.250
You lost focus. Again.

04:59.370 --> 05:00.210
Raise your hand.

05:00.540 --> 05:01.380
Stand firm.

05:01.900 --> 05:02.740
Continue.

05:18.050 --> 05:18.890
Zhao,

05:20.140 --> 05:22.220
martial arts are
to protect those beside you.

05:23.810 --> 05:24.900
Though facing death,

05:25.410 --> 05:26.700
it's for the sake of life.

05:27.410 --> 05:28.580
Do you understand?

06:18.250 --> 06:19.580
Aunt...

06:37.410 --> 06:40.100
Give Zigui's ashes to your mother.

06:41.100 --> 06:42.620
Ask her to take them back to Jiangdong

06:43.220 --> 06:45.060
and scatter them
by the graves of his parents.

06:45.610 --> 06:47.170
When you return to Luoying Valley,

06:47.410 --> 06:49.100
light incense for your aunt
on my behalf.

06:50.050 --> 06:50.890
Tell her

06:53.100 --> 06:54.980
we live well here.

06:56.439 --> 06:58.392
Our descendants
no longer practice martial arts.

06:58.490 --> 06:59.330
From now on,

07:00.250 --> 07:01.290
we have nothing more to do

07:02.730 --> 07:03.700
with Jianghu.

07:04.660 --> 07:05.580
It's a desolate place,

07:05.930 --> 07:07.020
nothing worth much.

07:07.490 --> 07:09.220
We brought you some food for the road.

07:10.900 --> 07:12.100
This treasured sword...

07:12.900 --> 07:14.490
A Qingque Sect disciple's blade.

07:14.850 --> 07:15.690
That's right.

07:16.220 --> 07:17.780
It was given to Zigui by Yin Dai

07:18.220 --> 07:19.446
when he first entered the sect.

07:20.290 --> 07:22.410
He once asked me to return it,

07:23.250 --> 07:25.050
saying he disgraced the sect

07:25.410 --> 07:27.176
and was unworthy
of being Master's disciple.

07:27.540 --> 07:28.380
He considered it

07:28.850 --> 07:29.730
as leaving the sect.

07:30.340 --> 07:31.180
From then on,

07:31.700 --> 07:32.810
he was no longer a disciple.

07:34.250 --> 07:35.090
Zhao,

07:35.370 --> 07:36.850
help deliver it as well.

07:50.730 --> 07:52.900
Uncle Guo must've been heartbroken.

07:53.580 --> 07:54.780
All these years,

07:54.780 --> 07:56.250
has he had a single happy day?

07:58.050 --> 07:58.890
That year,

07:59.250 --> 08:01.100
when he heard Pingshu
killed Nie Hengcheng,

08:01.730 --> 08:02.900
Zigui was still very pleased.

08:03.580 --> 08:05.370
His heart for upholding justice

08:06.370 --> 08:07.930
never completely turned cold.

08:09.290 --> 08:10.130
Uncle Shi,

08:10.490 --> 08:12.220
my mother once told me

08:12.540 --> 08:13.700
that when Aunt traveled,

08:13.700 --> 08:15.706
she befriended many friends
outside the Six Sects.

08:16.370 --> 08:18.100
Was there anyone special among them?

08:18.410 --> 08:19.370
Also,

08:19.370 --> 08:21.020
when Aunt went alone to the duel,

08:21.660 --> 08:22.540
where were they?

08:23.220 --> 08:24.193
Why didn't they help her?

08:24.850 --> 08:27.370
Back then, over half
of the Six Sects' elites perished.

08:27.370 --> 08:28.210
As for the rest,

08:28.700 --> 08:30.980
Yin Dai strictly ordered them not to go.

08:31.850 --> 08:34.180
Those close to your aunt
and skilled in martial arts

08:34.490 --> 08:35.783
were ambushed one after another.

08:36.060 --> 08:36.940
Some died;

08:36.940 --> 08:37.780
some were crippled.

08:38.940 --> 08:40.420
Pingshu had no choice.

08:41.010 --> 08:42.250
Was it Nie Hengcheng?

08:42.490 --> 08:43.650
It could not have been him.

08:44.530 --> 08:46.530
When Lu Chengnan stole
the Jade Sunflower,

08:46.820 --> 08:48.220
Nie Hengcheng was greatly shaken,

08:48.610 --> 08:49.450
nearly mad.

08:49.596 --> 08:51.989
Fearing discovery by his followers
and the righteous sects,

08:52.060 --> 08:53.182
he secluded himself to heal.

08:53.730 --> 08:55.610
He had no time to set ambushes.

08:55.610 --> 08:57.060
Mu is right.

08:57.420 --> 08:59.610
Pingshu also believed
it wasn't Nie Hengcheng.

08:59.890 --> 09:01.340
The culprit

09:02.100 --> 09:03.530
remains unknown to this day.

09:04.700 --> 09:06.180
It must've been the demonic sect.

09:07.250 --> 09:09.250
We've left Jianghu behind,

09:09.890 --> 09:11.060
but you are still within it.

09:11.980 --> 09:13.133
Old causes are hard to end;

09:13.300 --> 09:14.520
good outcomes are hard to reap.

09:14.650 --> 09:15.490
The Six Sects

09:15.690 --> 09:17.420
are deeply entangled
with the demonic sect.

09:17.420 --> 09:18.650
You two young people

09:19.370 --> 09:20.650
must take care of yourselves.

09:23.020 --> 09:25.780
(Qinglong Altar)

09:25.850 --> 09:27.586
Still playing with the peacock?

09:27.597 --> 09:29.490
The Young Master has been out
for over a month.

09:29.490 --> 09:30.523
Not going to look for him?

09:31.130 --> 09:33.490
He's likely being lovey-dovey

09:33.890 --> 09:34.730
with Miss Cai.

09:35.130 --> 09:36.276
Why would we go disturb them?

09:36.370 --> 09:38.370
Let him take his time.

09:38.770 --> 09:39.650
No rush.

09:39.650 --> 09:41.810
What if they truly elope?

09:44.530 --> 09:45.370
Unlikely.

09:46.130 --> 09:47.180
If they did,

09:48.580 --> 09:49.490
not only our Li Sect,

09:50.200 --> 09:51.890
but all the Six Sects would mobilize.

09:51.930 --> 09:53.769
Besides, the Young Master
has grand ambitions.

09:53.820 --> 09:54.820
To defy the world

09:55.010 --> 09:57.010
and ruin his future for love

09:57.300 --> 09:59.250
is not something he would do.

09:59.730 --> 10:00.570
Future?

10:01.940 --> 10:03.850
If Miss Cai likes it,

10:03.850 --> 10:06.850
I think he'd pluck stars
and seize the moon.

10:06.850 --> 10:08.530
A mere future and reputation

10:08.530 --> 10:10.340
mean nothing to him.

10:13.060 --> 10:14.060
Then I'll go look.

10:14.060 --> 10:14.900
Hurry up.

10:16.680 --> 10:17.530
What is it?

10:17.530 --> 10:18.536
Hu Fengge was taken away.

10:19.010 --> 10:19.850
What?

10:22.980 --> 10:23.906
Another persimmon cake.

10:29.300 --> 10:30.586
Still thinking about your aunt?

10:31.130 --> 10:32.180
How could I not?

10:33.130 --> 10:34.770
She knew Yin Dai's intentions

10:35.580 --> 10:37.650
yet still chose to go alone.

10:39.060 --> 10:40.130
No helpers,

10:41.270 --> 10:42.300
no support.

10:43.340 --> 10:44.250
She...

10:44.530 --> 10:46.250
Nie Hengcheng and Yin Dai are dead.

10:47.010 --> 10:48.060
Those who harmed your aunt

10:48.300 --> 10:49.180
are gone.

10:49.820 --> 10:50.660
No.

10:51.059 --> 10:52.545
There is still the skin-painted demon

10:52.610 --> 10:53.580
and the man in black.

11:02.300 --> 11:04.266
Could the skin-painted demon
be the man in black?

11:05.010 --> 11:07.130
He retrieved the saliva with my aunt

11:08.100 --> 11:09.820
and knew about the Jade Sunflower.

11:09.820 --> 11:12.100
He approached her with ulterior motives.

11:12.100 --> 11:13.650
His scheming mind

11:13.650 --> 11:14.580
and vast knowledge

11:15.010 --> 11:16.340
are unfathomable.

11:17.820 --> 11:19.130
But one thing is certain.

11:19.130 --> 11:20.370
He is from your Li Sect.

11:20.890 --> 11:21.730
There is

11:22.850 --> 11:25.220
no record of such a person.

11:26.220 --> 11:28.060
If the man in black is
the skin-painted demon,

11:28.340 --> 11:30.130
he should've obtained
the Jade Sunflower.

11:30.130 --> 11:31.730
Why slaughter the Chang clan?

11:33.060 --> 11:34.130
Uncle Shi said

11:34.940 --> 11:36.042
the mechanisms of Chang Fort

11:36.053 --> 11:37.493
changed their core every three years.

11:38.010 --> 11:39.340
Without someone guiding the way,

11:40.340 --> 11:41.180
no one

11:41.940 --> 11:43.340
could break in.

11:44.940 --> 11:46.650
How did the man in black enter?

11:46.850 --> 11:47.690
In recent years,

11:47.905 --> 11:49.558
the only outsiders
who entered Chang Fort

11:49.610 --> 11:50.450
were Ms. Luo

11:51.820 --> 11:53.010
and me.

11:57.730 --> 12:01.060
She was injured at Taichu Temple.

12:01.420 --> 12:03.580
Why did she later appear at Chang Fort?

12:05.580 --> 12:06.610
It was as if someone

12:07.220 --> 12:09.250
deliberately let Uncle Chang see her.

12:10.180 --> 12:11.163
As I once said,

12:11.174 --> 12:13.130
among the killers
who slaughtered the Chang clan,

12:13.130 --> 12:14.340
one emitted the Ethereal

12:14.340 --> 12:15.820
of Taichu Temple.

12:15.820 --> 12:17.370
I was certain it was Qiu Yuanfeng,

12:18.250 --> 12:19.940
but I ignored Wang Yuanjing beside him.

12:21.130 --> 12:22.550
But why would Wang Yuanjing do this?

12:25.770 --> 12:26.610
Zhao,

12:27.300 --> 12:28.770
didn't Uncle Shi say

12:29.130 --> 12:30.723
Wang Yuanjing and Mr. Guo Zigui

12:30.734 --> 12:32.547
were both imprisoned
in the EightClaw Prison?

12:33.530 --> 12:34.770
Uncle Guo was captured,

12:35.610 --> 12:37.100
yet Wang Yuanjing walked out.

12:37.610 --> 12:38.730
At that time,

12:40.340 --> 12:42.250
Mr. Wu was also imprisoned there.

12:43.130 --> 12:43.970
You mean

12:44.300 --> 12:46.130
Wang Yuanjing saw Wu Yuanying,

12:46.580 --> 12:47.850
yet didn't rescue him?

12:49.650 --> 12:50.490
Zhao,

12:51.610 --> 12:53.130
did you find it strange

12:53.130 --> 12:54.770
when Mr. Wu lunged

12:54.770 --> 12:56.820
at Wang Yuanjing

12:56.820 --> 12:57.890
at the memorial?

13:02.130 --> 13:02.970
Yuanying!

13:05.250 --> 13:06.980
Mr. Wu's expression

13:07.250 --> 13:08.980
didn't look like joy at reunion,

13:11.530 --> 13:12.980
but rather...

13:19.850 --> 13:20.770
Hatred.

13:40.300 --> 13:41.140
Zhao,

13:41.300 --> 13:42.610
you're finally back.

13:42.610 --> 13:44.100
We thought you were taken by Mu...

13:45.220 --> 13:46.060
Well.

13:46.980 --> 13:49.700
Mr. Mu took you for a stroll,

13:49.700 --> 13:51.340
and you had too much fun to return.

13:51.730 --> 13:53.060
- Chicken?
- Xingjia,

13:53.060 --> 13:53.980
where are the others?

13:53.980 --> 13:55.130
They are looking for you too.

13:55.700 --> 13:56.850
Ever since you and Mr. Mu

13:57.370 --> 13:59.250
went for that stroll,

13:59.250 --> 14:00.410
this place has been in chaos.

14:01.220 --> 14:02.300
What happened?

14:11.370 --> 14:13.300
Someone leaked news

14:13.300 --> 14:15.340
that you eloped with Mr. Mu.

14:15.340 --> 14:17.180
Now, not only are your parents here,

14:17.180 --> 14:19.375
but even Yang Heying,
Lord Yang, who thrives on chaos,

14:19.386 --> 14:20.820
came to watch the show.

14:21.180 --> 14:22.940
Master has a splitting headache.

14:22.940 --> 14:24.010
Whoever leaked it

14:24.850 --> 14:25.940
is a jerk!

14:26.300 --> 14:27.780
Yes, a jerk!

14:30.410 --> 14:31.250
Fan,

14:31.250 --> 14:33.250
did Song Yuzhi truly cancel
the betrothal?

14:33.580 --> 14:34.420
Absolutely.

14:35.420 --> 14:36.820
He said to follow the natural cause,

14:37.340 --> 14:38.793
but he couldn't hold back after all.

14:39.890 --> 14:40.730
What do you mean?

14:41.770 --> 14:42.890
Exactly what it sounds like.

14:47.490 --> 14:48.770
You two,

14:49.410 --> 14:50.250
what is going on?

14:50.250 --> 14:51.770
What's going on?

14:52.420 --> 14:53.370
Nothing is going on.

14:53.370 --> 14:54.210
Back to business.

14:55.220 --> 14:57.100
We think Taichu Temple is suspicious.

14:57.370 --> 14:58.610
You've been staying here lately.

14:58.610 --> 14:59.723
Have you seen Wang Yuanjing?

15:00.530 --> 15:01.490
Not much.

15:02.130 --> 15:03.610
All affairs in the temple

15:03.610 --> 15:05.220
are handled by Mr. Li Min.

15:05.580 --> 15:07.130
Lord Wang is rarely seen.

15:07.980 --> 15:09.010
Fan,

15:09.010 --> 15:11.180
what kind of person is Lord Wang?

15:12.340 --> 15:14.010
The incident with Ms. Luo Yuanrong

15:14.010 --> 15:15.370
hit him hard.

15:15.370 --> 15:18.130
After all,
three fellow disciples died at once.

15:18.130 --> 15:20.340
Who would not be upset?

15:21.420 --> 15:23.010
After returning from Qingque Sect,

15:23.010 --> 15:24.610
he immersed himself in alchemy

15:24.610 --> 15:25.490
and cultivation,

15:25.490 --> 15:26.890
claiming to have

15:26.890 --> 15:28.340
seen through worldly matters

15:28.340 --> 15:29.770
and seeking transcendence.

15:31.010 --> 15:31.850
Transcendence?

15:32.940 --> 15:34.490
He just fears vengeful spirits.

15:38.100 --> 15:39.010
Zhao,

15:39.010 --> 15:40.490
is there a problem with Lord Wang?

15:40.850 --> 15:41.690
A big one.

15:42.060 --> 15:43.700
But it's only a suspicion for now.

15:44.220 --> 15:45.130
If we want proof,

15:45.130 --> 15:46.530
he must admit it himself.

15:47.250 --> 15:49.130
We need to get close to him

15:49.130 --> 15:50.770
without arousing suspicion.

15:50.770 --> 15:52.490
He rarely meets guests.

15:52.490 --> 15:54.490
How can juniors like us approach him?

15:55.850 --> 15:56.883
Isn't he afraid of death?

15:57.580 --> 15:58.610
Then I think

15:58.610 --> 16:00.610
he would be interested in an elixir

16:01.010 --> 16:01.850
of immortality.

16:05.900 --> 16:10.140
(Taichu Temple)

16:18.650 --> 16:21.130
The Rebirth Pill?

16:21.610 --> 16:24.420
Uncle Lei spent
over ten years refining it,

16:24.420 --> 16:26.850
wasting countless herbs
to produce this single pill.

16:26.850 --> 16:29.340
It's said that taking it

16:29.340 --> 16:31.490
can free one from the three realms

16:31.490 --> 16:34.490
and ascend to transformation
like Founder Beichen.

16:34.850 --> 16:36.490
I was curious.

16:36.850 --> 16:40.060
Lord Wang, I heard you study alchemy,

16:40.060 --> 16:41.220
so I quietly

16:41.220 --> 16:43.060
brought it for you to examine.

16:43.060 --> 16:44.300
Is it truly that miraculous?

16:48.180 --> 16:49.700
Indeed, good medicine.

16:55.580 --> 16:57.010
Oh, my back...

17:00.610 --> 17:03.700
Xiuming's medical skills have improved.

17:24.090 --> 17:25.090
In two hours,

17:25.940 --> 17:26.940
we can enter.

17:44.180 --> 17:45.290
Yuanjing.

17:45.730 --> 17:46.980
Yuanjing,

17:48.220 --> 17:50.140
I can't die in peace.

17:50.140 --> 17:50.980
Don't come closer.

17:52.330 --> 17:53.220
Yuanjing.

17:54.250 --> 17:55.330
Yuanjing,

17:56.530 --> 17:59.730
when I sent a pigeon letter
to Taichu Temple,

17:59.730 --> 18:01.380
why did you ignore my plea?

18:01.380 --> 18:02.490
It didn't concern me.

18:02.490 --> 18:03.490
Not me.

18:03.490 --> 18:06.490
Did you hear the screams of my family?

18:06.490 --> 18:07.810
It wasn't me, Chang.

18:07.810 --> 18:09.490
- I'm innocent.
- My clan was killed.

18:09.490 --> 18:11.330
I can't die in peace.

18:11.980 --> 18:12.860
Yuanjing,

18:12.860 --> 18:14.530
why didn't you save me?

18:14.530 --> 18:15.490
Yuanying,

18:15.490 --> 18:17.490
you died because of Qiu Yuanfeng.

18:17.490 --> 18:18.980
He ignored you,

18:19.940 --> 18:20.810
not me.

18:20.810 --> 18:24.570
The EightClaw Prison.

18:37.420 --> 18:38.260
Yuanying,

18:38.770 --> 18:40.050
you're alive.

18:40.860 --> 18:41.940
I'll rescue you now.

18:58.180 --> 18:59.420
Yuanfeng said

19:00.010 --> 19:01.940
you were killed by Elder Kaiyang.

19:04.490 --> 19:06.010
Everyone thought you were dead.

19:07.180 --> 19:08.290
Master is gone;

19:08.810 --> 19:10.050
Uncle is invalid.

19:11.660 --> 19:14.330
Yuanfeng's cultivation
is far inferior to mine.

19:17.010 --> 19:17.900
They all said

19:20.490 --> 19:23.660
I'd be the next lord of Taichu Temple.

19:24.980 --> 19:26.490
As long as you were gone,

19:28.010 --> 19:31.570
I could return home in glory as the lord

19:31.886 --> 19:33.143
and bring honor to my ancestors.

19:34.810 --> 19:35.650
Yuanying,

19:36.940 --> 19:38.490
thanks for your help.

20:00.180 --> 20:02.380
To conceal your filthy deeds,

20:02.730 --> 20:05.140
you indirectly caused Guo Zigui's death.

20:05.420 --> 20:07.940
Ironically, when you returned
to Taichu Temple,

20:07.940 --> 20:10.530
you found Qiu Yuanfeng
inherited Uncle's cultivation

20:11.010 --> 20:12.620
and beat you

20:12.620 --> 20:14.250
during the sect competition.

20:14.620 --> 20:16.980
The lord position never came to you.

20:17.250 --> 20:19.420
That petty Qiu Yuanfeng

20:20.420 --> 20:24.220
flattered Uncle endlessly
during recovery

20:24.220 --> 20:26.730
and gained half his lifetime's power.

20:26.730 --> 20:28.570
You went for wool and came home shorn,

20:28.570 --> 20:31.490
leaving yourself vulnerable to others.

20:31.490 --> 20:34.140
For that single thought,
you regretted it for over a decade,

20:34.140 --> 20:35.220
yet you didn't repent

20:35.220 --> 20:37.290
and caused over 100 deaths
in the Chang clan.

20:37.290 --> 20:38.140
It wasn't me.

20:40.220 --> 20:41.980
The demonic sect did it.

20:41.980 --> 20:44.180
Who led them inside?

20:44.180 --> 20:45.770
Who deceived Yuanrong?

20:45.770 --> 20:48.660
Who opened Chang Fort's mechanisms

20:48.660 --> 20:50.490
- and caused the massacre?
- It wasn't me.

20:52.220 --> 20:54.180
I never meant to kill.

20:54.730 --> 20:56.010
I did not.

20:56.330 --> 20:57.620
Why didn't you save Yuanying?

20:57.620 --> 20:58.620
Why didn't you save him?

20:58.620 --> 20:59.460
Let go!

21:03.940 --> 21:05.380
Expel her.

21:05.380 --> 21:06.220
Yes.

21:10.250 --> 21:12.860
If you don't want your mistake exposed,

21:12.860 --> 21:14.220
do as I say.

21:19.500 --> 21:20.620
(Chang Fort)
Who is there?

22:00.180 --> 22:01.570
I never meant to kill them.

22:02.530 --> 22:03.810
I did not.

22:03.810 --> 22:05.290
He forced me.

22:06.490 --> 22:07.490
If I didn't comply,

22:08.250 --> 22:10.860
he'd tell everyone about my mistake.

22:11.490 --> 22:12.330
Chang,

22:12.490 --> 22:14.770
I only led them there.

22:18.860 --> 22:19.900
Who is the man in black?

22:28.770 --> 22:29.610
Who are you?

22:30.090 --> 22:31.330
What poison did you give me?

22:32.380 --> 22:33.490
Who am I?

22:35.050 --> 22:35.980
I'm Chang Ning.

22:37.900 --> 22:38.740
No.

22:39.420 --> 22:41.490
You are Mu Qingyan,

22:42.050 --> 22:43.196
who impersonated Chang Ning.

22:43.290 --> 22:44.130
Guards!

22:44.940 --> 22:46.090
Mr. Wu and Ms. Luo

22:46.090 --> 22:47.250
treated you as family,

22:48.420 --> 22:50.250
yet you caused their tragic deaths.

22:50.700 --> 22:52.220
Mr. Chang treated you well,

22:53.476 --> 22:55.416
yet you caused his entire can
to be slaughtered.

22:55.660 --> 22:57.620
You deserve the most tragic end.

22:58.420 --> 22:59.260
If he dies,

22:59.450 --> 23:01.090
no one will know
who the man in black is.

23:07.290 --> 23:08.130
Lord Wang.

23:12.940 --> 23:13.860
The Chaos Needle.

23:14.180 --> 23:15.530
You have it.

23:15.530 --> 23:17.220
Better not act rashly again.

23:17.220 --> 23:18.060
If you do,

23:18.700 --> 23:19.833
I won't be able to stop him.

23:19.980 --> 23:22.250
It seems you truly wish to die.

23:22.250 --> 23:23.130
Very well.

23:23.140 --> 23:24.620
I imagine the underworld

23:25.420 --> 23:28.220
has many waiting to claim your life.

23:30.490 --> 23:31.330
Cai Zhao,

23:31.810 --> 23:33.420
as a disciple of the Six Sects,

23:33.420 --> 23:34.810
you collude with a fiend.

23:35.330 --> 23:38.770
Are you not afraid of shaming
your master and parents?

23:39.530 --> 23:40.420
So what?

23:41.530 --> 23:42.810
I'll simply tell the truth.

23:43.250 --> 23:44.620
At worst, we gather everyone

23:44.620 --> 23:46.810
and lay out your ugly deeds

23:46.810 --> 23:48.380
one by one.

23:48.380 --> 23:50.140
You left Mr. Wu in that prison,

23:50.140 --> 23:52.090
set a trap for Ms. Luo,

23:52.090 --> 23:53.490
and caused Uncle Chang's death.

23:53.490 --> 23:54.330
Nonsense.

23:54.730 --> 23:55.660
No one will believe you.

23:56.050 --> 23:56.890
Lord Wang,

23:57.290 --> 23:59.330
I refuse to believe no one saw you

24:00.220 --> 24:01.620
take Ms. Luo to Chang Fort.

24:02.620 --> 24:04.290
If we investigate carefully,

24:04.290 --> 24:05.530
we will find witnesses.

24:06.250 --> 24:07.700
Would you like to try?

24:09.900 --> 24:10.770
Wang Yuanjing,

24:10.770 --> 24:12.530
if you tell me the name
of the man in black,

24:13.140 --> 24:14.490
I can spare your life.

24:14.490 --> 24:15.940
You may continue as the Lord.

24:16.620 --> 24:19.010
I won't mention the past.

24:19.010 --> 24:21.010
We go our separate ways.

24:21.010 --> 24:22.730
Why would you spare me?

24:23.940 --> 24:26.010
The one who slaughtered the Chang clan

24:27.180 --> 24:28.770
wasn't you, but that man in black.

24:29.050 --> 24:31.220
I only want to find him and kill him

24:31.530 --> 24:33.090
to avenge the Chang clan.

24:33.090 --> 24:34.570
As for Mr. Wu

24:34.570 --> 24:35.530
and Guo Zigui,

24:36.810 --> 24:38.360
I have no interest

24:38.371 --> 24:39.693
in your Six Sects' petty schemes.

24:40.200 --> 24:41.050
Think about it.

24:41.050 --> 24:42.730
If that person dies,

24:42.730 --> 24:44.860
you lose someone
holding leverage over you.

24:45.220 --> 24:46.660
Isn't that perfect?

24:47.010 --> 24:48.700
As long as you tell us his name,

24:49.330 --> 24:50.170
I guarantee

24:51.620 --> 24:52.530
he won't kill you.

24:55.860 --> 24:56.700
Fine.

24:58.290 --> 24:59.130
I'll tell you.

25:00.250 --> 25:01.940
Though he covered his face,

25:03.220 --> 25:05.620
I recognized his eyes.

25:07.620 --> 25:08.660
He is...

25:14.940 --> 25:15.780
He is outside.

25:16.860 --> 25:19.330
Seize the assassin!

25:28.900 --> 25:30.050
- Watch them.
- Yes.

25:32.730 --> 25:33.570
Lord Wang!

25:34.940 --> 25:36.490
They killed Lord Wang.

25:36.490 --> 25:37.330
Wait.

25:39.570 --> 25:40.490
We didn't kill him.

25:41.860 --> 25:42.700
Mu Qingyan,

25:42.900 --> 25:44.860
Chief of the demonic sect.

25:45.490 --> 25:46.380
You know me?

25:46.700 --> 25:49.140
I saw you in Qingque Town.

25:49.810 --> 25:50.650
Cai Zhao,

25:50.900 --> 25:52.140
as a disciple of the Six Sects,

25:52.660 --> 25:53.973
why collude with the demonic sect

25:53.984 --> 25:55.010
and murder our lord?

25:55.010 --> 25:57.620
What right does she have
to collude with me?

25:59.250 --> 26:00.330
She's merely

26:02.490 --> 26:04.250
a hostage I seized.

26:05.090 --> 26:06.290
Do you think I'd believe that?

26:06.770 --> 26:07.610
Cai Zhao,

26:08.490 --> 26:10.220
don't think you can clear yourself.

26:10.620 --> 26:11.570
Speak.

26:11.570 --> 26:13.180
Why did you kill our lord?

26:13.180 --> 26:14.330
He was scum.

26:15.330 --> 26:16.700
I killed him.

26:17.050 --> 26:18.530
What can you do?

26:18.530 --> 26:19.730
Outrageous.

26:19.730 --> 26:20.660
I'll kill you.

26:24.490 --> 26:25.330
You can touch me,

26:26.250 --> 26:27.270
but why touch my hostage?

26:27.660 --> 26:28.700
What are you waiting for?

26:28.700 --> 26:29.860
Avenge Lord Wang!

26:29.860 --> 26:31.220
Stop! Stop!

26:31.770 --> 26:32.730
Zhao!

26:33.050 --> 26:33.890
My father is here.

26:34.330 --> 26:35.180
I'll be fine.

26:35.180 --> 26:36.020
Go first.

26:38.220 --> 26:39.660
(Alchemy Room)

26:41.660 --> 26:42.500
Father.

26:43.980 --> 26:44.820
Mother.

26:53.940 --> 26:57.060
(Nie Zhe contacted a mole
and rescued Hu Fengge.)

27:02.060 --> 27:04.540
(Taichu Temple)

27:07.140 --> 27:09.090
I knew he wasn't dead.

27:11.050 --> 27:12.050
Zigui

27:12.730 --> 27:13.776
had always been like that.

27:14.810 --> 27:16.570
If he made a mistake,

27:16.570 --> 27:18.090
he'd hide somewhere outside.

27:18.940 --> 27:20.980
I kept waiting for him to come back.

27:20.980 --> 27:22.290
I thought

27:22.290 --> 27:23.730
even if he didn't show himself,

27:25.140 --> 27:26.900
he must be living well

27:28.420 --> 27:30.140
in some remote mountains.

27:30.730 --> 27:31.810
Who knew...

27:33.380 --> 27:34.330
Stop crying.

27:34.900 --> 27:37.140
Zhao said he passed peacefully.

27:37.140 --> 27:38.980
He settled what needed settling.

27:38.980 --> 27:40.570
Isn't that all life amounts to?

27:40.570 --> 27:41.530
That is enough.

27:41.530 --> 27:42.980
Are you even human?

27:42.980 --> 27:44.076
Didn't you hear Zhao say

27:44.087 --> 27:45.420
he was tortured beyond recognition

27:45.420 --> 27:46.770
by Nie Hengcheng's men

27:47.420 --> 27:49.940
and suffered for over a decade
on his sickbed?

27:51.140 --> 27:52.290
You call that peaceful?

27:53.130 --> 27:53.860
Enough.

27:53.871 --> 27:55.700
A traitor who surrendered
to the demonic sect

27:55.700 --> 27:57.455
managed to live
for over a decade in hiding.

27:57.466 --> 27:58.570
That was already fortune.

27:58.570 --> 27:59.644
Had he dared show himself,

28:00.050 --> 28:02.490
Lord Yin would've punished him
by the rules.

28:02.490 --> 28:03.660
Enough chatter.

28:06.290 --> 28:08.330
I know a little
about the Piercing Strike

28:08.860 --> 28:09.940
of the demonic sect,

28:09.940 --> 28:11.730
but I'm having a hard time mastering it.

28:11.730 --> 28:13.490
What luck running into you today.

28:13.490 --> 28:14.770
Come. Spar with me.

28:14.770 --> 28:15.980
Cai Pingchun, are you crazy?

28:15.980 --> 28:17.380
You crossed the line first.

28:17.380 --> 28:18.730
Let's see if this strike

28:18.730 --> 28:20.050
can hurt you.

28:20.050 --> 28:21.140
Then do it. Why waste words?

28:21.140 --> 28:22.530
- Come on.
- Stop!

28:27.010 --> 28:29.750
Yuanjing's body still lies here,

28:30.700 --> 28:32.380
yet as elders,

28:32.380 --> 28:33.810
you bicker before the juniors.

28:34.770 --> 28:36.250
Stop embarrassing yourselves.

28:36.250 --> 28:37.620
Thank you, Lord Qi,

28:37.620 --> 28:39.180
for remembering our slain lord.

28:39.180 --> 28:40.090
I'm incompetent.

28:41.090 --> 28:43.220
Lord Qi, please uphold justice
for Lord Wang

28:43.980 --> 28:45.290
and punish the true culprit

28:45.290 --> 28:47.660
to give all Taichu Temple disciples
an explanation.

28:50.810 --> 28:51.663
Master,

28:51.674 --> 28:53.387
you need not fear
Taichu Temple's trouble.

28:53.570 --> 28:54.490
I did nothing wrong.

28:55.420 --> 28:56.260
Wang Yuanjing

28:56.490 --> 28:57.380
deserved death.

28:57.700 --> 28:58.540
Zhao,

28:58.810 --> 28:59.700
stop.

28:59.700 --> 29:01.260
Li, don't worry.

29:01.730 --> 29:04.420
I know you shared deep ties
with your lord.

29:05.010 --> 29:07.810
But dismissing the other disciples

29:07.810 --> 29:09.050
and keeping matters quiet

29:09.420 --> 29:10.810
is also for your lord's sake.

29:10.810 --> 29:12.620
Lord Song, what do you mean?

29:12.620 --> 29:14.770
Didn't you hear Zhao?

29:15.330 --> 29:17.620
If Lord Wang truly left Mr. Wu
in that prison...

29:17.620 --> 29:18.980
That's slander

29:19.620 --> 29:21.900
from that demonic fiend.

29:21.900 --> 29:23.050
Who'd believe it?

29:23.530 --> 29:24.730
As everyone knows,

29:24.741 --> 29:26.836
Uncle Wang was always kind,
gentle, and magnanimous.

29:28.330 --> 29:29.170
Cai Zhao,

29:30.010 --> 29:32.860
you must've colluded
with Mu Qingyan to kill him.

29:33.290 --> 29:34.130
Li,

29:34.980 --> 29:36.730
we examined Lord Wang's sword wound.

29:37.250 --> 29:39.810
The swordsman possessed
immense inner force,

29:39.810 --> 29:41.290
beyond Zhao's ability.

29:41.770 --> 29:43.730
Even Mu Qingyan
may not have such cultivation.

29:46.700 --> 29:48.046
The demonic sect has many masters.

29:48.810 --> 29:49.700
Who knows

29:49.700 --> 29:51.180
if it was someone else?

29:51.700 --> 29:52.540
Cai Zhao,

29:53.570 --> 29:54.940
killing was bad enough,

29:55.810 --> 29:57.570
yet you smear Lord Wang's name.

29:57.570 --> 29:59.050
What is your intent?

29:59.530 --> 30:00.620
I do have intent.

30:02.570 --> 30:03.660
Everyone, do you remember

30:04.420 --> 30:06.380
that at Founder Beichen's memorial,

30:06.770 --> 30:07.610
how Mr. Wu reacted

30:08.050 --> 30:10.570
when Lord Wang approached Mr. Wu,

30:11.220 --> 30:12.940
whose meridians were severed?

30:12.940 --> 30:13.780
I remember.

30:13.980 --> 30:15.810
He could not see,

30:15.810 --> 30:18.250
but upon hearing Lord Wang's voice,
he raised his head,

30:18.250 --> 30:20.730
identified the direction, and lunged.

30:21.810 --> 30:23.220
He seemed extremely agitated.

30:27.380 --> 30:28.250
Zhao,

30:28.250 --> 30:29.420
you mean

30:29.890 --> 30:30.770
he wasn't falling

30:30.770 --> 30:32.490
into Wang Yuanjing's arms?

30:32.920 --> 30:33.810
He wanted...

30:33.810 --> 30:35.420
He wanted to bite Wang's throat.

30:37.250 --> 30:38.620
That does seem so.

30:39.490 --> 30:42.530
If Mr. Wu tried
to bite him before dying,

30:42.530 --> 30:43.660
Wang Yuanjing

30:43.660 --> 30:45.330
must have wronged him.

30:45.770 --> 30:47.940
When Wang Yuanjing entered
the EightClaw Prison,

30:49.490 --> 30:51.250
Wu was alive and well.

30:52.090 --> 30:53.730
Had he been saved then,

30:54.180 --> 30:56.330
he wouldn't have suffered later.

30:56.730 --> 30:57.570
Yeah.

30:57.980 --> 30:58.820
How tragic.

30:59.620 --> 31:00.860
With a few words,

31:01.730 --> 31:03.620
you condemn Lord Wang?

31:04.250 --> 31:05.090
So now,

31:05.770 --> 31:08.330
Mu Qingyan is righteous,

31:08.330 --> 31:10.660
and Lord Wang is evil?

31:10.660 --> 31:11.500
You

31:12.180 --> 31:13.420
simply bully Taichu Temple

31:13.420 --> 31:14.420
in its decline.

31:14.980 --> 31:15.860
Li,

31:15.860 --> 31:17.050
the Six Sects are as one.

31:17.490 --> 31:19.900
There is no bullying.

31:20.770 --> 31:23.770
If Lord Wang truly committed
such disgrace,

31:24.380 --> 31:27.140
the Six Sects would not shield him.

31:27.900 --> 31:28.740
Fine.

31:29.620 --> 31:31.380
Even if he failed to save someone,

31:33.900 --> 31:35.570
it wasn't a capital crime.

31:35.900 --> 31:36.980
Let me ask you.

31:38.620 --> 31:40.050
If he conspired with the man in black

31:40.900 --> 31:43.380
and caused over 100 deaths
in the Chang clan,

31:43.980 --> 31:45.010
does he deserve death?

31:45.010 --> 31:46.129
Enough of this man in black.

31:46.860 --> 31:49.180
A grand-master in black?

31:49.180 --> 31:50.810
You made him up.

31:50.810 --> 31:52.380
It's your conspiracy.

31:53.380 --> 31:54.220
Li,

31:54.900 --> 31:56.700
to know the truth,

31:56.700 --> 31:59.570
we need only find Mu Qingyan.

32:00.380 --> 32:01.570
For now,

32:02.180 --> 32:04.250
let Lord Wang be laid to rest.

32:05.180 --> 32:06.020
All matters

32:06.420 --> 32:08.530
will be discussed after the funeral.

32:09.860 --> 32:11.260
Yuzhi, Zhao,

32:12.090 --> 32:12.930
come with me.

32:24.010 --> 32:24.850
Stop.

32:26.250 --> 32:27.810
Taichu Temple

32:27.810 --> 32:29.770
won't let Cai Zhao leave!
She's the murderer!

32:38.420 --> 32:40.050
You shield your own.

32:40.530 --> 32:42.399
Whether she colluded with Mu Qingyan

32:42.410 --> 32:44.180
and killed Lord Wang
requires investigation.

32:44.180 --> 32:45.700
She can't leave.

32:45.700 --> 32:47.250
Of course, it will be investigated.

32:48.570 --> 32:50.620
But Zhao can't stay here.

32:50.940 --> 32:53.090
If she doesn't stay here,
what if she runs?

32:53.420 --> 32:54.260
Lady Ning,

32:54.940 --> 32:57.770
she's disappeared before, right?

32:59.700 --> 33:01.010
Zhao is my disciple.

33:01.380 --> 33:02.660
I guarantee for her.

33:03.050 --> 33:04.900
Until the matter is clear,

33:05.180 --> 33:07.140
she won't leave Qingque Sect.

33:07.660 --> 33:08.700
Li, refrain

33:09.490 --> 33:10.770
from reckless words.

33:15.490 --> 33:16.330
Taichu Temple

33:17.250 --> 33:18.380
is still among the Six Sects.

33:18.940 --> 33:20.380
As head of the Six Sects,

33:21.010 --> 33:22.250
I'm not decoration.

33:31.290 --> 33:32.290
Mind yourself.

33:32.860 --> 33:33.700
Let's go.

33:46.140 --> 33:48.140
I've warned you repeatedly

33:48.140 --> 33:50.140
that Mu Qingyan is no good man,

33:50.140 --> 33:51.290
but you refused to listen.

33:51.900 --> 33:53.380
You were deceived by him

33:53.380 --> 33:55.090
and ended up like this.

33:55.090 --> 33:57.050
Do you know how the Six Sects' disciples

33:57.050 --> 33:59.090
speak of you in private?

34:00.180 --> 34:01.020
Master,

34:02.180 --> 34:03.860
I left alone

34:03.860 --> 34:05.770
to seek the Shi brothers

34:05.770 --> 34:07.180
for news of the Jade Sunflower

34:07.810 --> 34:08.780
to heal Yuzhi.

34:09.090 --> 34:10.260
Traveling with Mu Qingyan

34:11.170 --> 34:13.490
was to investigate
the skin-painted demon.

34:13.780 --> 34:14.620
Also,

34:15.380 --> 34:17.690
the killer in the hall
was not Mu Qingyan.

34:17.690 --> 34:18.650
It was the man in black.

34:18.650 --> 34:19.740
I saw him myself.

34:19.740 --> 34:21.470
Did Mu Qingyan also say

34:21.481 --> 34:23.260
that the man in black
is from our Six Sects?

34:24.010 --> 34:25.170
Have you considered

34:25.170 --> 34:28.050
that everything you saw
may have been an illusion,

34:28.050 --> 34:30.340
arranged by Mu Qingyan?

34:31.900 --> 34:34.210
With a nonexistent man in black,

34:34.210 --> 34:36.780
he sows distrust among the Six Sects.

34:36.780 --> 34:38.130
This is

34:38.130 --> 34:40.050
a brilliant move indeed.

34:40.530 --> 34:42.050
I'll say it once more.

34:42.940 --> 34:43.980
The skin-painted demon

34:45.300 --> 34:47.010
can never be trusted.

34:54.010 --> 34:55.130
I heard Luoying Valley

34:55.130 --> 34:56.090
produces demonesses.

34:56.530 --> 34:58.980
This one is like her ancestor,

34:59.420 --> 35:01.340
colluding with the demonic sect chief

35:01.340 --> 35:02.646
and killing Taichu Temple's lord.

35:03.420 --> 35:04.490
Such scum.

35:04.490 --> 35:06.210
Yet Lord Qi still protects her.

35:07.010 --> 35:08.650
She colluded with the demonic sect

35:08.650 --> 35:10.490
and betrayed her sect.

35:10.490 --> 35:11.860
She should be executed

35:11.860 --> 35:12.700
to set an example.

35:14.780 --> 35:15.860
Who are you

35:15.860 --> 35:17.060
to slander Qingque Sect?

35:18.170 --> 35:19.010
This girl...

35:20.130 --> 35:21.050
She has a quick temper.

35:21.490 --> 35:22.610
Please forgive her.

35:22.610 --> 35:24.260
The demoness rumor is false.

35:24.820 --> 35:26.050
Spreading rumors is unwise.

35:28.900 --> 35:30.050
He is Song Yuzhi,

35:30.050 --> 35:31.300
Lord Qi's third disciple.

35:31.300 --> 35:32.140
What are you doing?

35:34.940 --> 35:35.780
Mr. Song,

35:36.050 --> 35:37.050
we meant no offense.

35:37.820 --> 35:38.660
Waiter.

35:38.680 --> 35:39.980
This table is on me.

35:40.010 --> 35:40.910
Sure.

35:40.910 --> 35:43.300
These gossipers

35:43.300 --> 35:44.740
deserve a lesson.

35:44.740 --> 35:46.900
That's just nonsense.

35:46.900 --> 35:48.300
- Ignore them.
- Exactly.

35:48.780 --> 35:50.120
Zhao hardly looks like a demoness.

35:52.490 --> 35:53.420
Cai Zhao,

35:53.420 --> 35:55.010
did you collude with Mu Qingyan?

35:55.010 --> 35:57.170
- Lingbo.
- You still defend her?

35:57.170 --> 35:59.300
Listen to what they say about us.

36:01.090 --> 36:01.906
Cai Zhao,

36:01.917 --> 36:03.666
if you truly colluded
with the demonic sect

36:03.677 --> 36:04.920
and shamed Father and the sect,

36:04.931 --> 36:06.490
I'll be the first to spare you no mercy.

36:06.490 --> 36:07.420
Lingbo,

36:07.420 --> 36:08.520
I didn't kill Wang Yuanjing.

36:09.380 --> 36:11.020
What's your relationship
with Mu Qingyan?

36:11.170 --> 36:13.050
Where did you go these past weeks?

36:15.820 --> 36:16.660
Master.

36:17.650 --> 36:18.490
Father.

36:18.650 --> 36:19.780
This is a critical time.

36:20.210 --> 36:21.170
As fellow disciples,

36:22.210 --> 36:23.780
you should stand together

36:23.780 --> 36:24.740
against a common foe.

36:24.740 --> 36:26.420
Yet look at yourselves.

36:28.300 --> 36:29.140
This entire matter

36:29.740 --> 36:31.050
began with Mu Qingyan.

36:31.340 --> 36:32.180
Your Uncle Li

36:32.490 --> 36:33.940
is pursuing him

36:34.570 --> 36:35.860
to give Taichu Temple justice.

36:36.300 --> 36:37.420
Until this is resolved,

36:37.860 --> 36:38.940
no one

36:39.650 --> 36:41.010
is to speak ill of Zhao.

36:41.220 --> 36:42.130
- Yes.
- Yes.

36:42.130 --> 36:42.980
Yes, Master.

36:44.210 --> 36:45.210
Especially you.

37:03.380 --> 37:04.220
Mother.

37:05.490 --> 37:07.340
This is my dowry prepared by Zigui.

37:07.740 --> 37:08.610
Keep it.

37:09.050 --> 37:10.940
You and Mu Qingyan saw him off.

37:11.420 --> 37:12.380
I have to thank you.

37:13.260 --> 37:15.090
Actually, we came today

37:15.090 --> 37:16.050
to talk

37:16.050 --> 37:17.570
with you.

37:17.570 --> 37:18.410
You want to ask

37:19.380 --> 37:21.340
about Mu Qingyan, right?

37:21.340 --> 37:22.380
Tell me the truth.

37:22.900 --> 37:23.860
Why did you

37:24.170 --> 37:25.490
go with him?

37:27.010 --> 37:28.610
We wanted to find

37:28.610 --> 37:30.380
who truly killed Uncle Chang.

37:30.900 --> 37:31.780
These weeks,

37:32.570 --> 37:33.410
how did he treat you?

37:51.650 --> 37:52.690
He treated me

37:54.940 --> 37:55.780
very well.

37:59.490 --> 38:00.650
And you?

38:05.170 --> 38:06.010
I...

38:08.130 --> 38:09.570
Do you like him?

38:18.200 --> 38:28.860
=Generation to Generation=

38:47.620 --> 38:52.030
♪The breeze is gentle,
and spring is fair♪

38:52.595 --> 38:57.210
♪I roam the rivers and hills
in the martial world♪

38:57.550 --> 39:02.115
♪With a shining cup,
I drink with delight tonight♪

39:02.640 --> 39:06.940
♪Free to wander in the world♪

39:09.885 --> 39:14.585
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

39:15.110 --> 39:19.400
♪I rest beneath the stars' soft gleam♪

39:20.060 --> 39:24.090
♪The night is calm, still as a stream♪

39:24.405 --> 39:29.530
♪It washes away all judgment and scheme♪

39:30.105 --> 39:34.915
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

39:35.130 --> 39:39.300
♪I hold the bright moon
as I return home♪

39:40.025 --> 39:43.960
♪I freely roam in the world♪

39:44.460 --> 39:49.735
♪All I ask is that you go with me♪

40:12.465 --> 40:17.595
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

40:17.960 --> 40:22.330
♪I hold the bright moon
as I return home♪

40:22.595 --> 40:26.725
♪I freely roam in the world♪

40:26.910 --> 40:32.485
♪All I ask is that you go with me♪
